 times   a b osborne hilary  february  barclays is uks most complained about bank new figures reveal the guardian london retrieved  february    statement of facts pdf united states department of justice  june  retrieved  july    a b c d barclays fined for attempts to manipulate libor rates bbc news  june  retrieved  june    a b barclays to pay largest civil fine in cftc history cbs news  june  retrieved  june    pollock ian  june  libor scandal who might have lost bbc news retrieved  june    barclays to pay over  million dollars to settle charges regarding libor xinhua news agency  june  retrieved  june    reuters  july  barclays chairman resigns over interest rate rigging scandal ndtv profit archived from the original on  july  retrieved  july    barclays boss bob diamond resigns amid libor scandal bbc  july  retrieved  july    bob diamond quits as barclays ceo philippine daily inquirer retrieved  april    executive profile antony p jenkins bloomberg business  june    three former barclays staff charged for alleged libor rates manipulation london mercury  february    ringshaw grant  december  barclays capital pays premium for women and minorities the daily telegraph london retrieved  july    barclays qatari capitalraising timeline euromoneycom  may     competition and regulatory matters – annual report  barclayscom   barclays in qatar loan probe financial times  january    revealed the truth about barclays and the abu dhabi investment euromoneycom  april    barclays needs to come clean about its gulf investments euromoneycom  april    us energy regulator orders barclays to pay £m fine the guardian  july   fca fines barclays mn pounds over gold price manipulation the london newsnet retrieved  may    dark pool fraud lawsuit filed against barclays in us new york telegraph retrieved  june    barclays seeks dismissal of new york dark pool suit the london newsnet retrieved  july    barclays credit suisse strike record deals with sec ny over dark pools reuters retrieved  