ys seeks dismissal of new york dark pool suit the london newsnet retrieved  july    barclays credit suisse strike record deals with sec ny over dark pools reuters retrieved  february    christopher m matthews  november  barclays to pay  million over ‘last look’ trading system wsj retrieved  march    press release retrieved  march    barclays in  mln us settlement over mutual funds reuters retrieved  february   referencesedit gamble audrey nona  a history of the bevan family london headley brothers oclc   raychaudhuri tappan irfan habib  dharma kumar eds  the cambridge economic history of india volume  cc cup archive isbn  top  world banks  the banker retrieved  april   amer sajed appointed chief executive of barclaycard  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to barclays official website barclays companies grouped at opencorporates v t e barclays division and subsidiaries barclays africa barclays canada barclaycard barclays investment bank barclays wealth historical components and acquisitions backhouses bank barclays private equity crossroads group firstcaribbean international bank gurneys bank juniper bank kuhn loeb  co martins bank lehman brothers lock hulme  co london provincial and south western bank the woolwich corporate directors john mcfarlane chairman sir gerry grimstone deputy chairman jes staley group chief executive chris lucas david booth alison carnwath fulvio conti simon fraser reuben jeffery iii sir andrew likierman dambisa moyo sir john sunderland other one churchill place category commons links to related articles v t e commercial and retail banks in the united kingdom banking in the united kingdom barclays barclays bank barclays wealth cybg clydesdale bank yorkshire bank hsbc holdings first direct hsbc bank hsbc private bank ms bank lloyds banking group bank of scotland bank of wales birmingham midshires halifax lloyds bank royal bank of scotland group adam and company child  co coutts  co drummonds bank natwest royal bank of scot